## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `ls -l public/storage` to verify the symlink.
- Check `storage/app/public` to verify files were moved correctly.

### Manual Verification
- Upload a new scholarship prospectus and verify it's stored in `storage/app/public` and viewable in the browser.
- Check existing scholarship images and icons on both frontend and admin panel to ensure they still load.
